Do you still hide anything

576
00:28:12,610 --> 00:28:14,740
about the case back then?

577
00:28:22,100 --> 00:28:23,870
I'm not hiding anything.

578
00:28:24,150 --> 00:28:25,430
I've investigated it afterward.

579
00:28:25,430 --> 00:28:26,150
Your men

580
00:28:26,150 --> 00:28:27,160
and the Japanese

581
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:29,090
were all looking for Ogura, who studied bacteria.

582
00:28:29,090 --> 00:28:29,950
But the car that hit you

583
00:28:29,950 --> 00:28:31,290
had a forged plate.

584
00:28:31,320 --> 00:28:33,380
The tenant of the house on Fuzhou Road was Wen Tian.

585
00:28:33,380 --> 00:28:34,680
He is your comrade.

586
00:28:34,700 --> 00:28:36,150
The materials and photos

587
00:28:36,150 --> 00:28:37,870
left at the explosion scene

588
00:28:37,870 --> 00:28:39,550
were all taken away by the Japanese Military Police.

589
00:28:39,550 --> 00:28:41,240
But I still have some.

590
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:42,470
I can submit them all

591
00:28:41,330 --> 00:28:43,600
[The first crime scene]

592
00:28:42,490 --> 00:28:43,950
and leave them for you to archive.

593
00:28:43,950 --> 00:28:45,270
Am I sincere enough?

594
00:28:53,790 --> 00:28:54,790
What about Ogura?

595
00:28:55,210 --> 00:28:57,380
Ogura was taken away by him.

596
00:28:57,420 --> 00:28:58,870
When I wanted to follow this line

597
00:28:58,870 --> 00:29:00,030
to investigate,

598
00:29:00,060 --> 00:29:02,440
people died one by one.

599
00:29:02,620 --> 00:29:05,150
I was forced to terminate the investigation.

600
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:13,030
Mr. Jin.

601
00:29:14,950 --> 00:29:16,080
Didn't Liu Mingjian

602
00:29:16,850 --> 00:29:18,310
threaten you all the time?

603
00:29:19,830 --> 00:29:20,710
We've solved

604
00:29:21,970 --> 00:29:23,320
this problem for you.

605
00:29:25,170 --> 00:29:26,470
[Accounts of Jin's Textile Factory]

606
00:29:28,030 --> 00:29:29,820
You killed him?

607
00:29:30,830 --> 00:29:32,820
This is a gift for you.

608
00:29:33,960 --> 00:29:35,890
Welcome back to the organization.

609
00:29:48,270 --> 00:29:49,450
Falcon.

610
00:29:50,850 --> 00:29:53,050
I don't want to contact you frequently.

611
00:29:54,350 --> 00:29:56,950
The police officers are also suspicious of me.

612
00:29:57,280 --> 00:30:00,230
I'm just a businessman. I had no choice.

613
00:30:00,910 --> 00:30:02,710
I don't want to get too involved.

614
00:30:07,020 --> 00:30:09,950
Mr. Jin, the older you get, the more confused you are.

615
00:30:17,270 --> 00:30:18,910
We solved your problem.

616
00:30:19,460 --> 00:30:21,660
Yet you asked the police to deal with us.

617
00:30:22,930 --> 00:30:25,590
Do you think the new government can support you?

618
00:30:32,300 --> 00:30:36,370
I was walking on the street today

619
00:30:36,940 --> 00:30:38,340
and picked up something.

620
00:30:40,370 --> 00:30:41,980
Do you know it?

621
00:30:49,650 --> 00:30:51,420
It should belong to

622
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:52,540
Jin Yan, right?

623
00:30:58,110 --> 00:31:00,590
Miss Jin Yan's room should be on the second floor,

624
00:31:00,590 --> 00:31:02,110
facing south on the right.

625
00:31:02,470 --> 00:31:04,970
Every morning at 5:30, she takes the No. 18 tram

626
00:31:04,970 --> 00:31:06,730
to go to the Public Security Bureau to work.

627
00:31:06,730 --> 00:31:08,390
If she doesn't work overtime,

628
00:31:10,320 --> 00:31:12,640
she'll get off work at 6:15 p.m. and get home at 7 p.m.

629
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:13,910
Today,

630
00:31:14,780 --> 00:31:18,400
she was wearing a beige shirt, a coffee-colored midi skirt,

631
00:31:19,530 --> 00:31:20,910
and brown high heels.

632
00:31:23,850 --> 00:31:25,320
I'm curious.

633
00:31:26,530 --> 00:31:28,930
How can you have such a beautiful daughter?

634
00:31:30,390 --> 00:31:31,590
I'm single, too.

635
00:31:34,060 --> 00:31:36,790
My daughter works at the Public Security Bureau?

636
00:31:38,510 --> 00:31:39,730
Mr. Jin.

637
00:31:41,080 --> 00:31:43,050
What a terrible father you are!

638
00:31:44,340 --> 00:31:46,740
Don't you know that

639
00:31:46,760 --> 00:31:47,720
Miss Jin Yan is a forensic doctor

640
00:31:47,720 --> 00:31:49,450
at the Public Security Bureau?

641
00:31:57,030 --> 00:31:58,640
What was the code name again?

642
00:32:01,170 --> 00:32:02,170
I remembered.

643
00:32:03,010 --> 00:32:03,840
It's Bulbul.

644
00:32:06,030 --> 00:32:08,640
Tell me. What do you want me to do?

645
00:32:09,320 --> 00:32:10,050
As long as...

646
00:32:12,100 --> 00:32:14,320
you don't…

647
00:32:16,780 --> 00:32:18,130
don't harm my daughter.

648
00:32:20,690 --> 00:32:22,550
Why did you make me sound so cruel?

649
00:32:22,720 --> 00:32:25,050
I'm just returning the thing she dropped.

650
00:32:25,550 --> 00:32:26,830
If anything happens,

651
00:32:27,190 --> 00:32:28,550
I'll let you know.

652
00:32:31,340 --> 00:32:32,010
Also,

653
00:32:35,120 --> 00:32:36,370
you're old.

654
00:32:37,060 --> 00:32:40,720
Don't resort to violence at the drop of a hat. It's inappropriate.

655
00:33:04,470 --> 00:33:06,870
Bulbuls are very protective of their baby.

656
00:33:07,110 --> 00:33:08,870
Sometimes, to protect their baby,

657
00:33:08,870 --> 00:33:10,610
they even dare to peck at people,

658
00:33:10,610 --> 00:33:12,410
disregarding their own safety.

659
00:33:13,040 --> 00:33:14,210
Unless he

660
00:33:15,390 --> 00:33:17,250
disregards his daughter's life.

661
00:33:18,020 --> 00:33:19,940
It's hard to say.

662
00:33:20,420 --> 00:33:23,020
Even threatened by the safety of his daughter,

663
00:33:24,110 --> 00:33:26,870
I'm afraid he won't obey orders easily.

664
00:33:27,700 --> 00:33:29,020
Don't worry.

665
00:33:30,100 --> 00:33:31,260
Bulbuls

666
00:33:32,320 --> 00:33:33,920
can't defeat the Falcon.

667
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:45,510
Give this money to Xu Wei.

668
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:48,460
I've accepted the murder of Liu Mingjian

669
00:33:48,490 --> 00:33:50,090
as his pledge of allegiance.

670
00:33:50,770 --> 00:33:52,450
He didn't do much for killing.

671
00:33:53,430 --> 00:33:55,490
Is it appropriate to give him so much?

672
00:33:58,830 --> 00:34:01,260
Money is indeed good.

673
00:34:01,790 --> 00:34:04,090
With just a little bit of it,

674
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:07,170
black can be turned into white.

675
00:34:07,480 --> 00:34:08,790
Sometimes, even a coward

676
00:34:08,790 --> 00:34:10,750
can become a warrior.

677
00:34:11,820 --> 00:34:12,760
Interesting.

678
00:34:20,270 --> 00:34:21,710
Give all of it to him.

679
00:34:22,540 --> 00:34:24,620
Change your old habits.

680
00:34:24,900 --> 00:34:27,630
Sure. I'll give him every penny.

681
00:34:31,909 --> 00:34:32,969
Then, what's next?

682
00:34:33,340 --> 00:34:34,870
Next, we need to figure out

683
00:34:34,870 --> 00:34:37,600
the background of the Hook Sword Gang at the wharf

684
00:34:38,030 --> 00:34:41,150
and how capable Dai Yueqing is.

685
00:34:41,170 --> 00:34:42,360
I'll do it now.

686
00:34:43,449 --> 00:34:44,560
Let Xu Wei go.

687
00:34:44,889 --> 00:34:46,960
You just keep an eye on Jin Maochang.

688
00:34:50,219 --> 00:34:51,050
Okay.

689
00:34:53,469 --> 00:34:55,530
Is it okay for you to just eat noodles?

690
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:10,780
You didn't come when we asked you to,

691
00:35:09,610 --> 00:35:13,490
[Case of Liu Mingjian]

692
00:35:11,420 --> 00:35:12,620
but now you came without informing us in advance.

693
00:35:12,620 --> 00:35:14,370
What do you take our Social Affairs Office for?

694
00:35:14,370 --> 00:35:15,730
Do you think it's a market?

695
00:35:15,730 --> 00:35:16,550
[Case of Liu Mingjian]

696
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:18,990
You're here too, Doggy.

697
00:35:19,040 --> 00:35:20,720
I didn't see you just now.

698
00:35:20,750 --> 00:35:22,750
I'll tell you again. My name is Huzi.

699
00:35:23,100 --> 00:35:25,230
If you go against me every day,

700
00:35:25,230 --> 00:35:26,840
I have to call you Doggy.

701
00:35:27,070 --> 00:35:29,220
The Military Control Commission has eight rules.

702
00:35:29,220 --> 00:35:31,220
You should know them better than me.

703
00:35:31,330 --> 00:35:32,750
It promised

704
00:35:32,830 --> 00:35:35,830
to retain the old police officers who have made contributions.

705
00:35:35,830 --> 00:35:37,030
I did.

706
00:35:37,240 --> 00:35:38,950
No one can deny that.

707
00:35:39,710 --> 00:35:40,660
Also,

708
00:35:41,020 --> 00:35:43,570
Chief Li Shiying called for a meeting

709
00:35:43,600 --> 00:35:45,490
to retain the former police.

710
00:35:45,520 --> 00:35:47,920
He said we can't let one single person who's

711
00:35:47,950 --> 00:35:49,790
willing to serve the people

712
00:35:49,790 --> 00:35:51,050
have no chance to work.

713
00:35:51,090 --> 00:35:53,660
I request to serve the people.

714
00:35:53,870 --> 00:35:56,190
You can't stop me from that, can you?

715
00:35:57,190 --> 00:35:58,310
I don't want to talk to you.

716
00:35:58,310 --> 00:36:02,320
[Case of Liu Mingjian]

717
00:35:58,500 --> 00:35:59,780
Then don't.

718
00:36:03,040 --> 00:36:03,860
Director Lu.

719
00:36:06,620 --> 00:36:07,310
Okay.

720
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:08,800
You can come back,

721
00:36:09,100 --> 00:36:11,230
but you're still a member of the auxiliary personnel.

722
00:36:11,230 --> 00:36:13,110
It doesn't matter.

723
00:36:14,930 --> 00:36:16,060
Then it's a deal.

724
00:36:16,080 --> 00:36:17,460
If you have any news about Xu Wei,

725
00:36:17,460 --> 00:36:19,150
let me know at any time.

726
00:36:19,170 --> 00:36:20,690
I should remind you.

727
00:36:21,300 --> 00:36:22,340
You have to be disciplined

728
00:36:22,340 --> 00:36:24,540
now that you've joined the Public Security Bureau.

729
00:36:24,540 --> 00:36:26,860
Okay. I'll let you all know

730
00:36:26,880 --> 00:36:28,840
as long as I have news about Xu Wei.

731
00:36:30,490 --> 00:36:31,290
Okay.

732
00:36:31,750 --> 00:36:33,480
Go through the procedures with

733
00:36:33,550 --> 00:36:35,110
some other colleagues tomorrow.

734
00:36:35,110 --> 00:36:36,570
There are other comrades?

735
00:36:37,860 --> 00:36:39,640
Director Lu, one more thing.

736
00:36:40,230 --> 00:36:40,780
Look.

737
00:36:41,150 --> 00:36:43,380
Now we have found this person,

738
00:36:43,510 --> 00:36:45,330
can Uncle Jin's name

739
00:36:45,350 --> 00:36:46,970
be cleared?

740
00:36:47,940 --> 00:36:48,630
Yes.

741
00:36:51,870 --> 00:36:53,150
It's late.

742
00:36:53,630 --> 00:36:54,710
You must be tired.

743
00:36:54,740 --> 00:36:56,000
Go back and rest early.

744
00:36:57,900 --> 00:36:59,450
Thank you, Xu.

745
00:37:00,040 --> 00:37:00,790
Come on.

746
00:37:00,830 --> 00:37:02,660
Let me help you pack.

747
00:37:03,070 --> 00:37:04,270
Where should I put it?

748
00:37:05,380 --> 00:37:05,930
[Case of Liu Mingjian]

749
00:37:07,270 --> 00:37:07,880
Lu.

750
00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:08,550
Wait for me.

751
00:37:10,640 --> 00:37:12,220
Jin Maochang's Textile Factory

752
00:37:12,220 --> 00:37:14,460
is making summer clothes for the Liberation Army.

753
00:37:14,460 --> 00:37:15,760
We have a strategic consideration.

754
00:37:15,760 --> 00:37:17,590
The production can't be affected.

755
00:37:17,590 --> 00:37:18,590
But Xu,

756
00:37:18,740 --> 00:37:20,690
we have to catch this person and close the case

757
00:37:20,690 --> 00:37:22,750
before we clear Jin Maochang's name.

758
00:37:23,510 --> 00:37:24,410
I'll look around a bit more.

759
00:37:24,410 --> 00:37:25,130
Bye.

760
00:37:33,180 --> 00:37:33,980
Yu,

761
00:37:34,500 --> 00:37:35,510
The glass is a bit dirty.

762
00:37:35,510 --> 00:37:36,630
I'll go get a towel.

763
00:37:36,930 --> 00:37:38,860
Go. There are not many people here.

764
00:37:44,200 --> 00:37:46,030
[No entry to the Storage Room for Unauthorized Personnel]

765
00:37:54,030 --> 00:37:55,430
Lan, it's me...

766
00:37:55,460 --> 00:37:57,220
Wei, you...

767
00:37:58,820 --> 00:38:00,190
Take the money.

768
00:38:00,220 --> 00:38:01,490
Go to the countryside to rest during pregnancy.

769
00:38:01,490 --> 00:38:02,750
Give birth to the baby.

770
00:38:04,930 --> 00:38:05,990
So much money.

771
00:38:07,250 --> 00:38:08,380
Where did you get it?

772
00:38:08,560 --> 00:38:09,880
What are you doing?

773
00:38:12,070 --> 00:38:13,350
If you can't tell me,

774
00:38:13,350 --> 00:38:14,350
go to Shaobai.

775
00:38:14,370 --> 00:38:15,270
He's looking for you

776
00:38:15,270 --> 00:38:16,230
He will help you.

777
00:38:16,230 --> 00:38:18,180
It's a special mission. Keep it a secret.

778
00:38:18,180 --> 00:38:20,440
Remember, don't trouble Shaobai.

779
00:38:20,450 --> 00:38:21,790
I'll solve my own problem.

780
00:38:21,790 --> 00:38:22,270
Wei.

781
00:38:22,270 --> 00:38:23,150
Trust me!

782
00:38:23,150 --> 00:38:25,660
Zhao Lan? She went to the storage room to get something.

783
00:38:25,660 --> 00:38:27,000
I need to go out.

784
00:38:29,540 --> 00:38:30,310
Go.

785
00:38:33,830 --> 00:38:34,940
[No entry to the Storage Room for Unauthorized Personnel]

786
00:38:36,350 --> 00:38:37,260
Sister-in-law.

787
00:38:37,060 --> 00:38:39,430
[No entry to the Storage Room for Unauthorized Personnel]

788
00:38:37,660 --> 00:38:39,780
Shaobai? What brings you here?

789
00:38:42,270 --> 00:38:43,630
I was just passing by,

790
00:38:43,660 --> 00:38:44,740
so I came to see you.

791
00:38:44,500 --> 00:38:46,040
[No entry to the Storage Room for Unauthorized Personnel]

792
00:38:44,760 --> 00:38:46,160
I brought you something.

793
00:38:46,960 --> 00:38:48,320
Don't bring anything anymore.

794
00:38:48,320 --> 00:38:50,520
We still have what you gave us last time.

795
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:51,440
It's okay.

796
00:38:53,530 --> 00:38:56,330
Wei is not here. Let me know if you need help.

797
00:38:59,040 --> 00:39:00,030
You didn't close the door.

798
00:39:00,030 --> 00:39:01,230
I'll close the door for you.

799
00:39:01,230 --> 00:39:02,030
You go ahead.

800
00:39:02,400 --> 00:39:03,300
Shaobai…

801
00:39:03,630 --> 00:39:05,350
Please get this pen for me.

802
00:39:05,350 --> 00:39:06,210
The second one.

803
00:39:44,170 --> 00:39:46,590
Sister-in-law. The lock is too old.

804
00:39:46,590 --> 00:39:47,720
Let me fix it for you.

805
00:39:51,380 --> 00:39:52,370
The second one.

806
00:39:54,080 --> 00:39:56,080
You're back. You even hid it from me.

807
00:39:56,400 --> 00:39:57,800
You're not a good friend.

808
00:40:04,430 --> 00:40:05,810
Listen carefully.

809
00:40:06,720 --> 00:40:08,430
No matter what you did,

810
00:40:08,570 --> 00:40:10,370
you'll always be my brother.

811
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:12,110
I've been investigating

812
00:40:12,110 --> 00:40:13,570
the textile factory case.

813
00:40:13,620 --> 00:40:15,400
I know that person is back.

814
00:40:18,030 --> 00:40:18,830
Xu Wei,

815
00:40:19,710 --> 00:40:21,840
if you still regard me as your brother,

816
00:40:21,960 --> 00:40:22,990
you must tell me

817
00:40:22,990 --> 00:40:24,190
what you need me to do.

818
00:40:24,780 --> 00:40:25,950
Even if the sky falls,

819
00:40:25,950 --> 00:40:27,550
we'll shoulder it together.

820
00:40:28,040 --> 00:40:28,910
Do you hear me?

821
00:40:34,850 --> 00:40:38,420
♫We've all been here; the lights are like the sun♫

