00:40:56,210 --> 00:40:57,860
♫The sky is high and the earth is thick♫

826
00:40:58,480 --> 00:40:59,790
♫Is it light or heavy?♫

827
00:40:59,810 --> 00:41:03,290
[No entry to the Storage Room for Unauthorized Personnel]

828
00:41:01,360 --> 00:41:04,740
♫I miss you in the wind, wandering about♫

829
00:41:02,160 --> 00:41:03,480
The lock is too old.

830
00:41:03,620 --> 00:41:05,350
I can't fix it, Sister-in-law.

831
00:41:05,680 --> 00:41:06,950
Tell the mall

832
00:41:06,950 --> 00:41:08,270
to get a new one.

833
00:41:08,120 --> 00:41:13,700
♫The light of the dawn goes through the palm♫

834
00:41:11,350 --> 00:41:12,150
I'm off, then.

835
00:41:15,060 --> 00:41:18,060
♫It shines on me and you♫

836
00:41:19,490 --> 00:41:23,950
♫Whose shadows are there?♫

837
00:41:28,370 --> 00:41:31,930
♫How can I forget?♫

838
00:41:32,580 --> 00:41:36,050
♫I can never forget♫

839
00:41:37,070 --> 00:41:40,580
♫The time when looked at each other♫

840
00:41:41,580 --> 00:41:42,510
Oh my!

841
00:41:42,510 --> 00:41:43,940
You're still sleeping?

842
00:41:45,040 --> 00:41:46,710
Aren't you going to work today?

843
00:41:46,710 --> 00:41:48,770
Get up. You're going to be late.

844
00:41:49,820 --> 00:41:50,660
Auntie.

845
00:41:49,870 --> 00:41:55,970
[Lin's Home]

846
00:41:51,110 --> 00:41:52,380
Give it to me.

847
00:41:52,400 --> 00:41:53,230
Coming.

848
00:41:54,230 --> 00:41:54,920
Here.

849
00:41:56,240 --> 00:41:57,260
Shaobai.

850
00:41:56,540 --> 00:42:01,710
[Lin's Home]

851
00:41:57,310 --> 00:41:59,380
This is your first day at work.

